summary: A level 1 nord, with no xp but has finished quests up to opening high hrothgar and nothing else. Good to start a new game without having to do the first couple of quests.
descriptionHtml:
A level 1 nord, with no XP (except half a level of lockingpicking) that has finished quests up to getting The Horn Of Jurgen Windcaller. So you'll have the full unrelenting force shout, whirlwind spirit (first word), 1 dragon soul and the golden claw quest item. As soon as you open the save you can progress like a brand new character.  Just open the console using ¬ then type "showracemenu" and you can create your own character thats completely blank. You'll have only 4 map markers: Riverwood, Whiterun, Whiterun Stables and High Hrothgar.

During the unbound quest, I followed hadvar into the keep. So you can go back to riverwood and talk to Alvor for a few extra items if you wanted them.

Requires all 3 DLC's (Who doesn't have them anyway?)

The only equipment you have is a small sum of gold and full iron armour with an iron sword and an iron shield, a few health potions and thats it.

Extract to your Skyrim saves folder (Mine is in My Documents/My Games/Skyrim)
author: Bethesda
